青桐高中成为 VTuber 机构/团体历史上第三个拥有 100 万订阅者的官方频道。 https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agcies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/ https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agcies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/#respondp2y_admin Sat, 27 Apr 2024 06:11:34 +0000 VTuberバーチャルTwitterYouTubeYouTuberあおぎり高校チャンネル登録者数(YouTube)バーチャルYouTuber https://p2y.jp/?p=123747 <p>截至2024年4月26日（令和6年）12点，VTuber团体青桐高中官方YouTube频道订阅人数已达100万，为VTuber机构和团体历史上第三位[…]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agencies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/">青桐高中成为 VTuber 机构/团体历史上第三个拥有 100 万订阅者的官方频道，该频道</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>截至2024年4月26日（令和6年）12点，VTuber团体<strong>青桐高中</strong>官方YouTube频道订阅人数已突破100万，成为历史上第三家VTuber机构/团体。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="674" data-attachment-id="123753" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agencies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/aogiri_high_school_became_the_3rd_vtuber_agencies_and_groups_in_history_to_reach_1_million_official_youtube_subscribers/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/aogiri_high_school_became_the_3rd_vtuber_agencies_and_groups_in_history_to_reach_1_million_official_youtube_subscribers.png" data-orig-size="1200,674" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="あおぎり高校 VTuber事務所・グループ史上3番目の公式チャンネル登録者数